    //
    // f(7) = k(7)(7).
    //   - Inner k(7) drives step_0 (Final): bind 7 to v, v+1 = 8,
    //     terminate DONE.
    //   - Layer 3a: tag=DONE → apply return arm. ret_fn(8): allocates
